profile:
Ivy Bloom's Home & Garden Inc. has established a strong reputation in the Comox Valley for the provision of landscaping services that are held to an extraordinarily high quality.

We hope that by conducting our business in a way that is both ethical and creative, we will be able to make a positive contribution to an increase in the overall standard and desirability of the Comox Valley.
name: Ivy Blooms Home & Garden Inc.
